# Gust

Gust is a wrapper of [tornado](https://www.tornadoweb.org/en/stable/). It allows for a hello world such as:

```python
from blueshed.gust import Gust, web

@web.get('/(.*)')
def get(request):
    """just a get"""
    return 'hello, world'

def main():
    """seperate construction from run"""
    Gust().run()

if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()
```

